---
layout: base.njk
pageTitle: About
extraStyles: |
  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  .about-header h1 {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  
  .about-header .role-tag {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: #666;
    background: #f5f5f5;
    border: 1px dashed #ccc;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  
  .about-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #fafafa;
    border: 2px solid #222;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .about-container::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 5px;
    left: 5px;
    right: -5px;
    bottom: -5px;
    border: 2px solid #222;
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0.15;
  }
  
  .profile-frame {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .profile-frame::before {
    content: '◇';
    position: absolute;
    top: -1rem;
    left: -1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #ccc;
  }
  
  .profile-pic {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border: 2px solid #222;
    filter: grayscale(20%);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  
  .profile-pic:hover {
    filter: grayscale(0%);
    transform: translate(-3px, -3px);
    box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 #222;
  }
  
  .about-text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .about-text p:first-letter {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #222;
  }
  
  .section-divider {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 3rem 0 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .section-divider::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    top: 50%;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #ccc, transparent);
  }
  
  .section-divider span {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #888;
  }
  
  .skills-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .skill-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    background: #fafafa;
    border: 2px solid #222;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
    min-width: 180px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  
  .skill-card:nth-child(odd) {
    transform: rotate(-0.5deg);
  }
  .skill-card:nth-child(even) {
    transform: rotate(0.5deg);
  }
  
  .skill-card:hover {
    transform: translate(-2px, -2px) rotate(0deg);
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #222;
  }
  
  .skill-card img {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: grayscale(30%);
  }
  
  .skill-card:hover img {
    filter: grayscale(0%);
  }
  
  .skill-card span {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #222;
  }
  
  .interests {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 2rem auto 0;
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  
  .interests strong {
    color: #222;
    font-style: normal;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .profile-frame {
      max-width: 250px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
---

<div class="about-header">
	<h1>{{ site.author }}</h1>
	<div class="role-tag">Game Developer</div>
</div>

<div class="about-container">
	<div class="profile-frame">
		<img src="/images/profile_pic.jpg" alt="Frank Yang" class="profile-pic">
	</div>
	<div class="about-text">
		<p>
			I'm a game developer with a Master's in Computer Science (Game Development) from USC. 
			I love crafting immersive experiences and exploring innovative mechanics. Some of my past 
			work focuses on prototyping game/XR mechanics, XR UX design, and game engine programming.
		</p>
		<p>
			Outside of game and XR development, you can find me playing video games (obviously :D), 
			playing and hosting escape rooms, and practicing magic tricks. Feel free to reach out – 
			I'm always excited to connect with fellow enthusiasts and collaborators!
		</p>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="section-divider">
	<span>Skills & Tools</span>
</div>

<div class="skills-grid">
	<div class="skill-card">
		<img src="/images/about/unity_logo.png" alt="Unity">
		<span>Unity</span>
	</div>
	<div class="skill-card">
		<img src="/images/about/csharp.png" alt="C#">
		<span>C#</span>
	</div>
	<div class="skill-card">
		<img src="/images/about/cplusplus.png" alt="C++">
		<span>C++</span>
	</div>
	<div class="skill-card">
		<img src="/images/about/3d_math.png" alt="3D Math">
		<span>3D Math</span>
	</div>
	<div class="skill-card">
		<img src="/images/about/blender_logo.png" alt="Blender">
		<span>Blender</span>
	</div>
</div>

<p class="interests">
	Also into <strong>escape rooms</strong>, <strong>magic tricks</strong>, and way too many <strong>video games</strong>.
</p>
